        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-serif italic text-glass-gray-600 dark:text-dark-glass-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto transition-colors duration-300">
          Need fractional product marketing leadership, a launch partner, or hiring a full-time growth lead? I help teams ship work that moves metrics and I'm open to the right in-house opportunity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Options Section -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 transition-colors duration-300">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-12">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-glass-gray-800 dark:text-dark-glass-gray-800 mb-4 transition-colors duration-300">
            Availability
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-glass-gray-600 dark:text-dark-glass-gray-600 transition-colors duration-300">
            Currently supporting venture-backed teams through fractional product marketing initiatives and exploring senior GTM leadership roles.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <article class="p-8 bg-glass-white/60 dark:bg-dark-glass-white/60 backdrop-blur-lg border border-glass-white/40 dark:border-dark-glass-white/40 rounded-glass shadow-soft hover:shadow-glass transition-all duration-300">
