            <p class="text-sm text-glass-gray-600 dark:text-dark-glass-gray-600 mb-5 transition-colors duration-300">
              Built for teams accelerating launches, lifecycle programs, and growth experiments that require measurable progress.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-glass-gray-600 dark:text-dark-glass-gray-600 transition-colors duration-300">
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-glass-primary dark:bg-dark-glass-primary"></span>
                <span>Fractional product marketing leadership and go-to-market strategy design.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-glass-primary dark:bg-dark-glass-primary"></span>
                <span>Messaging, positioning, and activation playbooks that demonstrate measurable growth.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-glass-primary dark:bg-dark-glass-primary"></span>
                <span>Hands-on execution embedded with product, sales, and revenue operations teams.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="p-8 bg-glass-white/60 dark:bg-dark-glass-white/60 backdrop-blur-lg border border-glass-white/40 dark:border-dark-glass-white/40 rounded-glass shadow-soft hover:shadow-glass transition-all duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-glass-gray-800 dark:text-dark-glass-gray-800 mb-3 transition-colors duration-300">Recruiter & Hiring Conversations</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-glass-gray-600 dark:text-dark-glass-gray-600 mb-5 transition-colors duration-300">
              Open to Director-plus product marketing, growth, or GTM leadership opportunities centered on building durable revenue engines.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-glass-gray-600 dark:text-dark-glass-gray-600 transition-colors duration-300">
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-glass-primary dark:bg-dark-glass-primary"></span>
                <span>Enterprise, AI, and automation portfolios preparing to scale adoption.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-glass-primary dark:bg-dark-glass-primary"></span>
                <span>Mandates that call for a builder comfortable across strategy and execution.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-glass-primary dark:bg-dark-glass-primary"></span>
                <span>References, case studies, and recent impact summaries available on request.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-center sm:space-x-8 space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 text-sm sm:text-base text-glass-gray-700 dark:text-dark-glass-gray-700">
          <a href="mailto:contrerasfrancisco@icloud.com" class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 hover:text-glass-primary dark:hover:text-dark-glass-primary transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
            <span>contrerasfrancisco@icloud.com</span>
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/contreras-francisco/" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 hover:text-glass-primary dark:hover:text-dark-glass-primary transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>linkedin.com/in/contreras-francisco</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Calendar Section -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 transition-colors duration-300">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-sans font-semibold text-glass-primary dark:text-dark-glass-primary mb-4 transition-colors duration-300">
            Schedule a Call
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-serif italic text-glass-gray-600 dark:text-dark-glass-gray-600 transition-colors duration-300">
            Prefer to talk live? Grab time to review a project scope, walk through an open role, or explore whether we're a fit.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Cal.com Embed -->
        <div class="bg-glass-white/60 dark:bg-dark-glass-white/60 backdrop-blur-lg border border-glass-white/40 dark:border-dark-glass-white/40 rounded-glass overflow-hidden shadow-soft hover:shadow-glass transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="relative h-[600px]">
            <!-- Cal inline embed code begins -->
            <div style="width:100%;height:100%;overflow:scroll" id="my-cal-inline-meet-contact"></div>
            <script type="module">
              const CAL_EMBED_ID = 'my-cal-inline-meet-contact';
              const SCRIPT_SRC = 'https://app.cal.com/embed/embed.js';

              const loadCalEmbed = () => {
                if (typeof window === 'undefined' || window.__calEmbedLoaded) {
                  return;
                }

                const embedRoot = document.getElementById(CAL_EMBED_ID);
                if (!embedRoot) {
                  return;
                }

                window.__calEmbedLoaded = true;

                (function (C, A, L) {
                  const p = function (a, ar) { a.q.push(ar); };
                  const d = C.document;
                  C.Cal = C.Cal || function () {
                    const cal = C.Cal;
                    const ar = arguments;
                    if (!cal.loaded) {
                      cal.ns = {};
                      cal.q = cal.q || [];
                      const script = d.createElement('script');
                      script.src = A;
                      script.defer = true;
                      script.referrerPolicy = 'strict-origin-when-cross-origin';
                      d.head.appendChild(script);
                      cal.loaded = true;
                    }
                    if (ar[0] === L) {
                      const api = function () { p(api, arguments); };
                      const namespace = ar[1];
                      api.q = api.q || [];
                      if (typeof namespace === 'string') {
                        cal.ns[namespace] = cal.ns[namespace] || api;
                        p(cal.ns[namespace], ar);
                        p(cal, ['initNamespace', namespace]);
                      } else {
                        p(cal, ar);
                      }
                      return;
                    }
                    p(cal, ar);
                  };
                })(window, SCRIPT_SRC, 'init');

                window.Cal('init', 'meet-contact', { origin: 'https://app.cal.com' });
                window.Cal.ns['meet-contact']('inline', {
                  elementOrSelector: `#${CAL_EMBED_ID}`,
                  config: { layout: 'month_view', theme: 'auto' },
                  calLink: 'francisco.contreras/meet',
                });
                window.Cal.ns['meet-contact']('ui', { hideEventTypeDetails: false, layout: 'month_view' });
              };

              const scheduleCalLoad = () => {
                const execute = () => {
                  if ('requestIdleCallback' in window) {
                    requestIdleCallback(() => loadCalEmbed(), { timeout: 2000 });
                  } else {
                    setTimeout(() => loadCalEmbed(), 100);
                  }
                };

                const embedRoot = document.getElementById(CAL_EMBED_ID);
                if (!embedRoot) {
                  return;
                }

                if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
                  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries, obs) => {
                    const isVisible = entries.some((entry) => entry.isIntersecting);
                    if (isVisible) {
                      obs.disconnect();
                      execute();
                    }
                  }, { rootMargin: '200px 0px' });
                  observer.observe(embedRoot);
                } else {
                  window.addEventListener('load', execute, { once: true });
                }
              };

              if (typeof window !== 'undefined') {
                scheduleCalLoad();
              }
            </script>
            <!-- Cal inline embed code ends -->
          </div>

          <style>
            [data-cal-embed] iframe {
              border-radius: 0 0 24px 24px;
            }

            [data-cal-embed] [class*='powered'],
            [data-cal-embed] [class*='branding'],
            [data-cal-embed] a[href*='cal.com'] {
              display: none !important;
              visibility: hidden !important;
              height: 0 !important;
              overflow: hidden !important;
            }
          </style>

          <!-- Contact Links at bottom of section -->
          <div class="p-6 border-t border-glass-white/30 dark:border-dark-glass-white/30 bg-glass-white/20 dark:bg-dark-glass-white/20">
            <div class="flex justify-center space-x-8">
              <a href="mailto:contrerasfrancisco@icloud.com" class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-glass-gray-600 dark:text-dark-glass-gray-600 hover:text-glass-primary dark:hover:text-dark-glass-primary transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium">contrerasfrancisco@icloud.com</span>
              </a>

              <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/contreras-francisco/" target="_blank" class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-glass-gray-600 dark:text-dark-glass-gray-600 hover:text-glass-primary dark:hover:text-dark-glass-primary transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium">LinkedIn</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
